  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support prisoner&apos;s children through story-telling</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pact works to reduce re-offending rates by helping to keep families together while a parent is imprisoned. The aim of &apos;Inside Stories&apos; is to strengthen the bond between imprisoned parents and their children by sharing and reading a story book together. This gives prisoner&apos;s children a chance to spend quality time with their parent when they come to visit them. Around 200,000 children per year in the UK have to cope with the hidden sentence of imprisonment of a parent and they need your support</narrative>
  </description>
